      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay so basically just the ointment then. if i do that for a few days and the redness stays the same, i'll just keep going with it right? i dont want to waste money on a doctor visit if the ointment is doing its job and clearing up the infection. it should be fine as long as i keep it clean and use the cream, yeah?",
